**Lycanthropic** | Attribute
__Basics__
The Lycanthropic player will have the attributes 'wolfish' and 'lycan' meaning their abilities will impact roles such as assistant or recluse as well as aura teller.

__Formalized__
Starting:
  • Apply `Wolfish` to @Self (~Attribute)
  • Apply `Lycan` to @Self (~Attribute)
